  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT THIS GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brawl with fists, swords, bows, and even boomerangs!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 Blaze through the battlefield using your Gauntlets 🔥</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/extras/796734bb590e6e9e0656cf6150fc7f5e.poster.avif?t=1752835647\" width=602 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/extras/796734bb590e6e9e0656cf6150fc7f5e.webm?t=1752835647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/extras/796734bb590e6e9e0656cf6150fc7f5e.mp4?t=1752835647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brazen Blaze is a high-speed VR multiplayer action game. Use your Gauntlets to smash through enemies and buildings! Master your 360° Boost Dash to soar through the skies as you aim to become the world’s strongest Runner!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >👊 Smash your enemies by any means necessary 👊</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/extras/130c4ecdd8e420a25505db634acad9e5.poster.avif?t=1752835647\" width=604 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/extras/130c4ecdd8e420a25505db634acad9e5.webm?t=1752835647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/extras/130c4ecdd8e420a25505db634acad9e5.mp4?t=1752835647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not only do you have your character's unique Gauntlet and weapons at your disposal, but also random items that appear on the battlefield to help take down your foes. Rocket launchers, illegal bats, beam sabers, and… energy drinks?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🚀 Destroy the stage 🚀</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/extras/f52ae75ba25fc366a0342fa440435d45.poster.avif?t=1752835647\" width=656 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/extras/f52ae75ba25fc366a0342fa440435d45.webm?t=1752835647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/extras/f52ae75ba25fc366a0342fa440435d45.mp4?t=1752835647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every building on the stage is destructible, allowing you to create your own battlefield advantage! But be warned! Buildings crumble during the fight, and stages fall apart over time, changing the course of the battle.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT THIS GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brawl with fists, swords, bows, and even boomerangs!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 Blaze through the battlefield using your Gauntlets 🔥</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/extras/796734bb590e6e9e0656cf6150fc7f5e.poster.avif?t=1752835647\" width=602 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/extras/796734bb590e6e9e0656cf6150fc7f5e.webm?t=1752835647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/extras/796734bb590e6e9e0656cf6150fc7f5e.mp4?t=1752835647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brazen Blaze is a high-speed VR multiplayer action game. Use your Gauntlets to smash through enemies and buildings! Master your 360° Boost Dash to soar through the skies as you aim to become the world’s strongest Runner!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >👊 Smash your enemies by any means necessary 👊</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/extras/130c4ecdd8e420a25505db634acad9e5.poster.avif?t=1752835647\" width=604 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/extras/130c4ecdd8e420a25505db634acad9e5.webm?t=1752835647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/extras/130c4ecdd8e420a25505db634acad9e5.mp4?t=1752835647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not only do you have your character's unique Gauntlet and weapons at your disposal, but also random items that appear on the battlefield to help take down your foes. Rocket launchers, illegal bats, beam sabers, and… energy drinks?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🚀 Destroy the stage 🚀</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/extras/f52ae75ba25fc366a0342fa440435d45.poster.avif?t=1752835647\" width=656 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/extras/f52ae75ba25fc366a0342fa440435d45.webm?t=1752835647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511050/extras/f52ae75ba25fc366a0342fa440435d45.mp4?t=1752835647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every building on the stage is destructible, allowing you to create your own battlefield advantage! But be warned! Buildings crumble during the fight, and stages fall apart over time, changing the course of the battle.</p>",
